<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich und Martin von Aufseß</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe des beschlagnahmten Viehs der Armleute in Zapfendorf des Günther Münzmeister, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_34" id="16v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_34_line_1576490423176_7534">Vlrichen vnd Mertein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l27">von <expan>Aufſeͣſʒe</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_34_r1l29">Lieben vlrich vnd Mertein / vns hat fürgelegt / <expan>Günth<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Müntʒmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l30">vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie Jr hanſen leͣſener / vnd <expan>Cuntʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Strauſʒ / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l31">auch <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan> anderen ſeinen Armenleuten <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> Jm cʒu CƷappffendoꝛff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l32">geſeſʒen etvvÿuiel vÿhs / <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>andere<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd gen Aufſeͣſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l33">getriben habt / das ſie <expan>auſʒgeʒaiche<ex>n</ex>t</expan> haben / vnd auch das mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l34"><expan>Jre<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten behaben wöllen / daʒ daſſelbe vÿhe Jr / vnd <expan>nÿema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l35">anders ſeÿ / <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan> / daʒ Ir <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Arme<ex>n</ex>leute</expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l36">daſſelb Jr vÿhe <expan>vngehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_34_r1l37">Als etc / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Gallj / Anno etc ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_34" id="16v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulrichen und Mertein von <expan>Aufseͣsze</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben Ulrich und Mertein, uns hat fürgelegt
                                                  <expan>Günth<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Münczmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, unser
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie ir Hansen
                                                Leͣsener und <expan>Cuncze<ex>n</ex></expan> Strausz
                                                und auch <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan> anderen
                                                seinen armenleuten <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> im
                                                czu Czappffendorff geseszen etwyviel vyhs
                                                  <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>andere<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und gen Aufseͣsz
                                                getriben habt, das sie
                                                  <expan>auszgezaiche<ex>n</ex>t</expan> haben, und
                                                auch das mit <expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten
                                                behaben wöllen, daz dasselbe vyhe ir und
                                                  <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> anders sey.
                                                  <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>leute</expan> dasselb ir vyhe
                                                  <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>en</ex></expan>, als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli anno etc. ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
